---
title: Brussels Sprout Mac & Cheese with Caramelised Onion and Cheesy Crumb
description: The most wonderful time of the year brings wonderful flavours too, and this Brussels Sprout Mac & Cheese with Caramelised Onion and Cheesy Crumb will be a delicious addition to any festive table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221018_R21_W51_UK_V12507-2_KB_Main_low-031db1e6.jpg
